# PDF Chatbot Assistant
This App allows users to upload PDF documents, process them to extract text, and interact with a chatbot that answers questions based on the content of the PDFs and using GPT model the chatbot generate the answers based on the document content.

## Features:
- Users can upload multiple PDF files.
- Extracts text from PDF documents using PyMuPDF.
- The extracted text is chunked and indexed using FAISS to enable fast similarity searches.
- Users can ask questions, and the chatbot retrieves relevant text from the uploaded PDFs to generate answers using Azure OpenAI's GPT model (gpt-4o). 


## Technologies Used:
Flask: Web framework to serve the application.
FAISS: Library for efficient similarity search and clustering of documents.
PyMuPDF: Used for extracting text from PDFs.
Azure OpenAI GPT: Used for generating chatbot responses using (gpt-4o) model based on document content. 
